web.footer.view_our_source_code_on_githu.en: View our source code on GitHub
web.footer.view_our_source_code_on_githu.translation: Oglejte si našo izvorno kodo na GitHub

web.footer.read_our_latest_blog_posts.translation: Preberite naše najnovejše objave na blogu

web.meta.were_making_onetime_secret_avai.en: We're making {onetime-secret} available in multiple languages. Since this is a new feature, you may encounter translation errors or awkward phrasing. Your feedback helps us improve - if you spot any issues, please {send-feedback}
web.meta.were_making_onetime_secret_avai.translation: Onetime Secret je na voljo v več jezikih. Ker je to nova funkcija, lahko naletite na napake v prevodu ali nerodno izražanje. Vaše povratne informacije nam pomagajo izboljšati - če opazite težave, {send-feedback}

web.meta.translations_are_new_spotted_an.en: Translations are new. Spotted an error? {send-feedback}
web.meta.translations_are_new_spotted_an.translation: Prevodi so novi. Opazili ste napako? {send-feedback}

web.meta.we_recently_added_translations.en: We recently added translations. Spotted an error? {send-feedback}
web.meta.we_recently_added_translations.translation: Nedavno smo dodali prevode. Opazili ste napako? {send-feedback}

web.meta.privacy_and_security_should_be_.en: Privacy and security should be accessible to everyone, regardless of language. We're adding translations to help both our users and their message recipients better understand how to safely use and access secure messages and links. Since this is a new feature, you might encounter some translation errors or unclear instructions. To help us improve the clarity and accuracy of our translations, especially for critical security-related content, please {send-feedback} if you spot any issues
web.meta.privacy_and_security_should_be_.translation: Zasebnost in varnost bi morali biti dostopni vsem, ne glede na jezik. Dodajamo prevode, da našim uporabnikom in njihovim prejemnikom sporočil pomagamo bolje razumeti, kako varno uporabljati in dostopati do varnih sporočil in povezav. Ker je to nova funkcija, lahko naletite na napake v prevodu ali nejasna navodila. Za pomoč pri izboljšanju jasnosti in točnosti naših prevodov, zlasti za kritično varnostno vsebino, {send-feedback}, če opazite težave

web.help.secret_view_faq.what_am_i_looki.en: You're viewing a secure message that was shared with you through Onetime Secret. This content is displayed only once and then permanently deleted from our servers.
web.help.secret_view_faq.what_am_i_looki.translation: Ogledujete si varno sporočilo, ki je bilo z vami deljeno preko Onetime Secret. Ta vsebina je prikazana samo enkrat in nato trajno izbrisana z naših strežnikov.

web.help.secret_view_faq.can_i_view_agai.en: Can I view this secret again later?
web.help.secret_view_faq.can_i_view_agai.translation: Ali lahko to skrivnost znova pogledam kasneje?

web.help.secret_view_faq.can_i_view_agai.en: No. For security reasons, this secret is only viewable once. After closing this page, the content will be permanently deleted and cannot be recovered by anyone, including us.
web.help.secret_view_faq.can_i_view_agai.translation: Ne. Iz varnostnih razlogov je ta skrivnost vidna samo enkrat. Po zaprtju te strani bo vsebina trajno izbrisana in je nihče, vključno z nami, ne bo mogel obnoviti.

web.help.secret_view_faq.how_to_copy.tit.en: How do I save this information?

web.help.secret_view_faq.how_to_copy.des.en: Use the 'Copy to Clipboard' button to copy the entire secret. For longer secrets, make sure to verify you've copied the complete content before leaving this page.
web.help.secret_view_faq.how_to_copy.des.translation: Uporabite gumb 'Kopiraj v odložišče' za kopiranje celotne skrivnosti. Za daljše skrivnosti se prepričajte, da ste kopirali celotno vsebino, preden zapustite to stran.

web.help.secret_view_faq.is_my_viewing_t.en: Is my viewing of this secret tracked?
web.help.secret_view_faq.is_my_viewing_t.translation: Ali se moj ogled te skrivnosti sledi?

web.help.secret_view_faq.is_my_viewing_t.en: The sender will be notified that their secret was viewed, but we don't track who viewed it or from what location. Your privacy is protected.
web.help.secret_view_faq.is_my_viewing_t.translation: Pošiljatelj bo obveščen, da je bila njegova skrivnost ogledana, vendar ne sledimo, kdo jo je ogledal ali od kod. Vaša zasebnost je zaščitena.

web.help.secret_view_faq.one_time_warnin.en: Once you leave or refresh this page, this secret will be permanently deleted and cannot be recovered by anyone.
web.help.secret_view_faq.one_time_warnin.translation: Ko zapustite ali osvežite to stran, bo ta skrivnost trajno izbrisana in je nihče ne bo mogel obnoviti.

web.layout.customize_your_app_preference.en: Customize your app preferences and settings
web.layout.customize_your_app_preference.translation: Prilagodite svoje preference in nastavitve aplikacije

web.layout.view_source_on_github.translation: Oglejte si izvorno kodo na GitHub
